  "detailed_description": "<h1>Cargo Remastered</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi! As the Cargo Remastered update is coming along nicely, I've decided to update the store page and I'll be pushing an update to the experimental branch here soon.<strong> To those that do not current own the game, this store page contains content that may not be released yet. Old screenshots will be available till the release of the Remastered Update.</strong></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE: MOST OF THIS DESCRIPTION APPLIES TO THE UPCOMING \"CARGO: REMASTERED\" UPDATE. SOME FEATURES MAY NOT BE IN THE CURRENT GAME.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Postal Worker. Your job is to deliver packages to the correct address.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the city. Interact with civilians, take a swim in the river, deforest the entire city (yes, you can do that).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DELIVER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and deliver packages to customers to earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SHOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the shop to purchase upgrades, tools, vehicles, and more!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE: MOST OF THIS DESCRIPTION APPLIES TO THE UPCOMING \"CARGO: REMASTERED\" UPDATE. SOME FEATURES MAY NOT BE IN THE CURRENT GAME.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Postal Worker. Your job is to deliver packages to the correct address.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXPLORE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the city. Interact with civilians, take a swim in the river, deforest the entire city (yes, you can do that).</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DELIVER</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and deliver packages to customers to earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SHOP</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Visit the shop to purchase upgrades, tools, vehicles, and more!</p>",
